#
#  normalize
#
#  A leetv utility program
#
#  Normalize the audio for a set of videos files.
#  Especially useful for commercials obtained from
#  diverse sources.
#
#  Last update: 2018-05-28
#
ffmpeg-normalize *.mp4 -c:a aac -b:a 192k -ext mp4 -v
